Package: didimpute
Title: Difference-in-Differences Imputation Estimator (Borusyak, Jaravel & Spiess)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Xao", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "xao@hbs.edu")
Description: A faithful R port of the Python did_imputation package implementing the
    imputation estimator of Borusyak, Jaravel and Spiess (2024) for staggered
    difference-in-differences, with event-study aggregation and plotting.
